    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors correctly scoped to Gradation 1 not-assessed status consistent with MRL 2 expectations per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 3. Discretization error exceeds minimum requirement at Gradation 3. Validation comparison confirms CFD predictions within 10% of experimental hemolysis measurements across the full COU operating envelope. The RH < 1 acceptance criterion is met at all operating conditions. The assessment team concludes the model has sufficient credibility to support the COU decision for this Class II CPB device.",
